{
  "id": "d-latch",
  "title": "D Latch (Data Latch)",
  "category": "memory",
  "description": "Stores a single bit. When the Enable input is ON the output Q tracks the D (Data) input. When Enable goes OFF, Q holds its last value. Built from an RS latch with AND gates gating the S and R lines from D and NOT(D).",
